    </p>
    <p>Sometimes, you have to wait to be seated, especially after 7PM. Sometimes, the weather is really hot, and the only free tables are on the patio outside. Sometimes, the parking lot is so full, you have to park in their backup lot, which is a lot farther away.
    </p>
    <p>But I have never, EVER, been dissatisfied with my meal at Lupe Tortilla.</p>
